snippet.title: Sphere - Flying Cities [PC] Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Sphere - Flying Cities is a sci-fi citybuilder which combines strategy, simulation, and survival elements in an extraordinary and immersive scenario.

More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/15555-sphere-flying-cities/

Sphere - Flying Cities is expected to launch on Steam Early Access in Fall 2021, with full launch scheduled for 2022.
